## üîß Configuration

### Adding New Apps

Edit the `APPS` dictionary in `PortalConfig`:

```python
class PortalConfig:
    APPS = {
        "My New App": {
            "file": "my_app.html",
            "description": "Description of my app",
            "height": 900
        }
    }
```

Or add dynamically:

```python
portal = HTMLPortal()
portal.add_app(
    name="Dynamic App",
    filename="dynamic.html",
    description="Added at runtime",
    height=800
)
```

### URL Parameters

Pass data to HTML apps:

```python
params = {
    "user": "john_doe",
    "session": "abc123",
    "theme": "dark"
}

portal.embed_app("My App", params=params)
```

HTML app receives: `my_app.html?user=john_doe&session=abc123&theme=dark`

