## üìÇ Static File Serving

### Local Development

Streamlit automatically serves files from your app directory:

- Place HTML files in `html_apps/` folder
- Access at: `http://localhost:8501/html_apps/your_file.html`

### Streamlit Cloud Deployment

1. Files in `html_apps/` are automatically deployed
1. Update `BASE_URL` in config to match your deployment URL:

```python
class PortalConfig:
    BASE_URL = "https://your-app.streamlit.app/html_apps/"
```

### External Hosting (Alternative)

Host HTML files elsewhere and point to them:

```python
class PortalConfig:
    BASE_URL = "https://your-github-pages.io/apps/"
```

